      <bioghist>
         <head>Biographical/Historical Information</head>
         <p>Pitts, Hankin &amp; Trundle/ J.L. Pitts &amp; Company were
         general contractors in Barber, Virginia specializing in
         highway construction.</p>
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent>
         <head>Scope and Content Information</head>
         <p>This collection consists of business records of the firms
         of J.L. Pitts, Jr. &amp; Brothers, Barber , Virginia (main
         office in Scottsville, Virginia), General Contractors
         specializing in highway construction, and Pitts, Hankin, and
         Trundle, Railroad Contractors of Prestonsburg, Kentucky. These
         papers contain ca. 600 accounts and receipts (2 Hollinger
         boxes) and thirteen bound volumes, including the following
         types of volumes: letterbook, daybook, ledger, journal,
         payroll records, time book, and shipment records.</p>
      </scopecontent>
